survey_response.review_text:
** ****** ** ** ********* ******* *** I would personally recommend her to all my family, relatives and friends. The clinic is so neat and beautiful and doesn’t look like other dentistry which i’ve Seen earlier. It is positive and feels comfortable when you sit for counselling with her to explain my problem. She is knowledgable with her work and explained the cause and care of teeth in a layman’s Language where I could even understand the medical terms. Her Handwork in using the tools for dental work is superb Because I did not get tired nor pain when she did the cleaning and polishing of my teeth.  

I also had my 5 year old daugther checked as she had two decays in both her grinder teeth. Initially I was wondering how a 5 year kid would react listening to the tools operating but Dr. Siddhi calmed and within no time she finished removing the decay and filled it up. Of course, my daugther cried due to sound of the tools but within 5 minute of dental filling done, she was all Happy and playing. 

Her hand stability is superb. Infact seeing her handle my kid, i asked her whether she has done Paediatric dentistry but she hasn’t. She is definitely super and recommended when I have to advise someone for dental care.

Thank you Dr. Siddhi for your Care and excellent work. All the best👍
